Display clear.
KernelInstaller fileInClassChunks: 'RecorzKernelClass: #MethodBlockArgumentReporter superclass: #Object instanceVariableNames: ''''
!
sum
    ^[ :x | x + 4 ] value: 3
!'.
Transcript show: 'MARG'.
Transcript cr.
Transcript show: ((((KernelInstaller classNamed: 'MethodBlockArgumentReporter') new) sum) printString).
Transcript cr.
